1. System will have to create a customer with a cutomer wallet
2. System will have to create some unique customer wallets related with a customer
3. System will have to charge money on a wallet to a customer
4. System will have to check the wallet status
5. System will have to show the user wallet movements to the user
6. System will have to create a commerce with a commerce wallet
7. System will have to transfer money from customer wallet to a commerce wallet